data.description: Update!!!! Seller to assist with a rate buy down to 5.87% or Closing cost assistance up to $14,500 at closing! Look at this sweet gem of a house, nestled beneath the beautiful mossy oak trees and beside the deep water of the East River!! See it now, 5 bedroom, 5 bathrooms 3768 sq ft of completely renovated space! Beautiful custom kitchen opened up to the cathedral ceilings!  Imagine creating lasting memories swimming in the swimming pool, hosting parties and get togethers in the pool house! Your guests have the comfort of a beautiful, resort style bathroom right beside the pool! Once you’re done with the pool pile everyone up in the boat for a fun boat ride down the river! Enjoy sunset picnics right from the comfort of your own back yard, or sitting on the private porch right off the primary bedroom!!  After a long day at work, take a steamy bath in the large tub!  Work from home?? Well look no more, there is awesome home office!!!  This home is truly a one of a kind piece of property that truly is an oasis right here in Camden County!!  TONS OF UPGRADES AND ADDITIONS!  See listing documents for a full list!!!  Call me 912.660.7041 for your showing! Please have active prequalification letter available to schedule showing
